          Academics
        </h1>
        <!-- Subheading with responsive text size and spacing -->
        <h2 class="mt-4 md:mt-6 text-xl md:text-3xl md:leading-12">
          IIITN students innovate and apply knowledge through
          <span class="inline md:block">
