          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Undergraduate Education</h2>
          <p class="mb-2 text-gray-700">
            Our undergraduate programs provide a strong academic foundation,
            encouraging innovation, research, and hands-on learning.
          </p>
          
          <!-- Programs & Specializations -->
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-6 mb-2">Programs & Specializations</h2>
          <p class="mb-2 text-gray-700">
